name: NU_InfluenzaTestsForNovelInfluenzaAVirusAntibodyByHemagglutinationInhibition
title: NU_Influenza (Tests for Novel influenza A virus Antibody by Hemagglutination Inhibition)
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with quantitative hemagglutination inhibition antibody tests for Novel Influenza A),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: component: influenza A virus hemagglutination; serogroups H2 and H4-H18;  

LOINC search: 'Influenza virus A (H2 or H4 or H5 or H6 or H7 or H8 or H9 or H10 or H11 or H12 or H13 or H14 or H15 or H16 or H17 or H18) Ab Method:HAI'),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
